Operation mindeset
==================
CMMI: Capability Maturity Model Integration (CMMI) is a process level improvement training and appraisal program. Administered by the CMMI Institute, a subsidiary of ISACA, it was developed at Carnegie Mellon University (CMU). It is required by many U.S. Government contracts, especially in software development.


Development  >  Test   >  Stage   > Preprod   > Production[ruuning application]


They are very stable, and they will follow process without fail.

