DevOps as solution:

Father of Devops: Patrick Dubois

Devopment Operations  > #DevOpsDay[formar name of Devops] > DevOps  > 5 principles

1) Development should respect operation team.

2) Operation team should respect development team.

3) Process should follow uniform process.

4) Automation.

5) CICD principles

